  "instructions": "<p>You can start hunting here as early as level 300 but it will improve as you get a few more levels. As you reach level 350 to 400 it will make it a lot more comfortable to box here. There is lots of room to run the creatures here so you can get them weakened before you begin your box. You will have to be careful in the few areas where you find Humongous Fungus though as they can make you drunk and could cause you to get trapped if you aren't prepared. It is possible to hunt this spawn with mana potions only but I preferred Great Spirit Potions to make boxing easier.&nbsp;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üí∞ Your profit can depend on the price of suspicious devices on your server. I was typically looting 10-15 Suspicious Devices per hour and they were worth 18k on my server at the time of recording.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üí∏ The cost to access the spawn makes it not a great area if you only have time for a quick 1 hour hunt. Though the profit will still cover the cost of entrance this becomes a better spawn when you are able to hunt for a longer duration, or return multiple times in the same 8 hour period as you'll only have to pay the entrance fee the once.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üêó This can be a good spawn for hunting task completions. I was killing around 600 to 650 Diremaws and 250-300 Deepworms per hour. Deepworms will be a little slower to complete but you will be able to complete an 800 kill task of Diremaws in just over an hour.&nbsp;</p>",
